column5: Here a cool video from last weeks open water trip to Quinte !!  Big walleyes !! Enjoy Greg
Those are some beauties for sure. Good job.
Can't beat a +8 to 10C day on New Years eve!! Some great fish there..
Great job, braving the weather. Something about purple that drives them wild.
Thanks for the video of the cool fish.   Art
SWEET!! Certainly had some great weather for the day.
Absolute delight to watch Great job you guys and thanks for sharing Leechman
WTG bud.  Now I am sitting here typing this message depressed and twitching waiting for soft water.  BF
Nice!!!!!! Some really nice Pickereyes there boys... thanks for posting! Shame about the background music! LOL HH
Fantastic.  That is as good as it can get.
Nice video! Maybe a little off with the music but to each their own . Rihanna and walleye are a funny mix
